He was a Hollywood heartthrob of the 1950s and 1960s appearing on the covers of hundreds of film magazines.
Hunter's film credits include Battle Cry (1955), The Girl He Left Behind (1956), Gunman's Walk (1958), and Damn Yankees (1958).
